(:summary    "Display line numbers to the left of buffers"
 :created    "2007"
 :updated    "2008"
 :license    "GPL-3"
 :authors    (("Markus Triska" . "markus.triska@gmx.at"))
 :maintainer ("Markus Triska" . "markus.triska@gmx.at")
 :provided   (linum)
 :keywords   ("convenience")
 :homepage   "http://stud4.tuwien.ac.at/~e0225855/linum/linum.html"
 :commentary "\
Display line numbers for the current buffer. Copy linum.el to your
load-path and add to your .emacs:

   (require 'linum)

Then toggle display of line numbers with M-x linum-mode. To enable
line numbering in all buffers, use M-x global-linum-mode.")
